US government

00:09:10.284 --> 00:09:12.450
to be able to launch a
satellite that would do that,

00:09:12.450 --> 00:09:13.950
and they're trying
to make the case,

00:09:13.950 --> 00:09:15.660
look, there's not
a lot more that's

00:09:15.660 --> 00:09:17.670
