mean you're going

00:09:18.730 --> 00:09:20.320
to be seeing faces
and things that

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:24.930
might be problematic from
a privacies prospective.

00:09:24.930 --> 00:09:27.990
Or particular
installations, that's

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:31.280
not going to make
a big difference.

00:09:31.280 --> 00:09:33.524
Now, we should
also mention we're

00:09:33.524 --> 00:09:35.940
